1
00:01:26,770 --> 00:01:30,990
=My Dear Guardian=

2
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:33,990
=Episode 8=

3
00:01:38,975 --> 00:01:39,875
Xiao Jun.

4
00:01:40,531 --> 00:01:43,281
Do you still like
Xuan Xuan from your school?

5
00:01:45,064 --> 00:01:46,084
What do you like about her?

6
00:01:46,697 --> 00:01:47,631
I like everything about her.

7
00:01:48,145 --> 00:01:49,216
Why?

8
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:52,440
Is she the prettiest girl in your school?

9
00:01:53,304 --> 00:01:54,360
I don't think so.

10
00:01:55,257 --> 00:01:56,837
Then why do you like her?

11
00:02:02,384 --> 00:02:04,353
Why did you suddenly ask me this?

12
00:02:09,809 --> 00:02:10,869
Luo Xiao Jun.

13
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,800
How do you feel?

14
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,379
What say you?

15
00:02:15,545 --> 00:02:17,965
I think you're doing really well.

16
00:02:19,915 --> 00:02:21,015
Xia Chu.

17
00:02:21,544 --> 00:02:23,054
Change his dressing.

18
00:02:23,165 --> 00:02:24,045
Yes.

19
00:02:26,992 --> 00:02:28,682
What are you doing?

20
00:02:29,225 --> 00:02:31,485
We're discussing about the next step.

21
00:02:31,696 --> 00:02:33,237
You're really in the mood.

22
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,680
All right. Let's go to Room 3.

23
00:02:40,933 --> 00:02:42,843
Is it so difficult to see a doctor?

24
00:02:44,703 --> 00:02:45,634
Let's go.

25
00:02:48,927 --> 00:02:51,157
Let's go.
It's time to see the psychiatrist.

26
00:02:53,878 --> 00:02:55,068
Don't mess with me.

27
00:02:56,825 --> 00:02:58,075
I'm not messing with you.

28
00:02:58,401 --> 00:03:00,661
-It's your turn.
-It's my turn.

29
00:03:01,425 --> 00:03:02,440
Liang Mu Ze.

30
00:03:07,337 --> 00:03:09,757
The white blood cell count
of patient no. 18 is still low.

31
00:03:10,514 --> 00:03:11,684
Pay attention to him.

32
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,340
If your family like it, just let me know.

33
00:03:14,381 --> 00:03:15,815
I can bring more for you.

34
00:03:15,856 --> 00:03:16,956
Don't be shy.

35
00:03:17,521 --> 00:03:18,651
What are you doing?

36
00:03:19,692 --> 00:03:20,672
Dr. Zhang.

37
00:03:21,174 --> 00:03:22,692
Don't sell it too hard.

38
00:03:22,733 --> 00:03:25,490
You're going to make our nurses
go bankrupt soon.

39
00:03:26,181 --> 00:03:27,115
That's impossible.

40
00:03:27,157 --> 00:03:29,757
These handmade reusable bag
are designed by me.

41
00:03:29,798 --> 00:03:31,672
-It's a present for the nurses.
-Is it?

42
00:03:31,721 --> 00:03:33,560
It's to thank them
for taking care of my son.

43
00:03:33,601 --> 00:03:35,148
Thank you so much.

44
00:03:35,189 --> 00:03:36,368
We're getting back to work.

45
00:03:36,409 --> 00:03:37,399
Thank you for the present.

46
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,259
You should get back to work. By the way,

47
00:03:39,827 --> 00:03:41,103
-it's for everyone.
-Thank you, Ms. Meng Zhen.

48
00:03:41,144 --> 00:03:43,194
The patterns and designs are my ideas.

49
00:03:43,235 --> 00:03:44,389
You won't find it anywhere else.

50
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,708
I hope you like it.

51
00:03:45,749 --> 00:03:46,859
Thank you.

52
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:48,000
You're welcome.

53
00:03:49,328 --> 00:03:50,508
I don't get one?

54
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,977
It's rare to see men buying reusable bag.

55
00:03:54,018 --> 00:03:55,040
Hence, I didn't make one for you.

56
00:03:56,592 --> 00:03:57,782
However,

57
00:03:58,279 --> 00:04:00,139
I know that doctors are hygienic.

58
00:04:00,368 --> 00:04:02,929
Therefore, I made you a soap.

59
00:04:03,141 --> 00:04:04,211
I hope you like it.

60
00:04:05,241 --> 00:04:06,541
You made a soap for me?

61
00:04:12,461 --> 00:04:14,891
Look, my surname is carved on the soap.

62
00:04:16,499 --> 00:04:17,378
Thank you so much.

63
00:04:17,419 --> 00:04:18,529
You're welcome.

64
00:04:18,570 --> 00:04:20,399
It's personally customized
and it's the only and only in the world.

65
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,409
-I'll keep it well.
-Sure.

66
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:24,798
By the way, we just checked on Xiao Jun.

67
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,008
He's recovering well.

68
00:04:26,049 --> 00:04:27,439
We changed his dressing today.

69
00:04:27,633 --> 00:04:29,839
If everything goes well,
he can be discharged on Monday.

70
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,820
Really?

71
00:04:31,529 --> 00:04:32,799
Thank you so much!

72
00:04:39,816 --> 00:04:40,756
Okay, got it.

73
00:04:41,248 --> 00:04:42,307
I'll come now.

74
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,828
There's a patient in the emergency ward.

75
00:04:44,869 --> 00:04:46,375
A metal pierced through his chest.

76
00:04:46,416 --> 00:04:47,461
I'm going down to have a look.

77
00:04:47,502 --> 00:04:48,903
Take care of your respective patients.

78
00:04:48,944 --> 00:04:51,154
-Call me if anything.
-Yes.

79
00:04:51,661 --> 00:04:52,510
Okay, you go ahead.

80
00:04:52,551 --> 00:04:54,128
Ms. Meng Zhen, we're getting back to work.

81
00:04:54,168 --> 00:04:55,640
Okay, go now.

82
00:05:00,829 --> 00:05:02,319
Have you fallen in love with someone?

83
00:05:02,508 --> 00:05:03,388
No.

84
00:05:03,673 --> 00:05:04,655
Say it.

85
00:05:04,696 --> 00:05:05,696
It's a secret between us.

86
00:05:05,737 --> 00:05:07,040
I won't tell Ms. Zhen.

87
00:05:08,041 --> 00:05:09,979
I'm not you. I'm not scared of your mom.

88
00:05:10,020 --> 00:05:11,116
Who are you scared of?

89
00:05:11,157 --> 00:05:12,187
I'm scared of you the most.

90
00:05:15,024 --> 00:05:15,904
Xiao Jun.

91
00:05:16,539 --> 00:05:17,689
It's time to change dressing.

92
00:05:20,009 --> 00:05:20,889
Here.

93
00:05:21,063 --> 00:05:22,193
Pull your shirt up.

94
00:05:24,982 --> 00:05:25,862
Let me help you.

95
00:05:26,147 --> 00:05:27,007
Go away!

96
00:05:27,048 --> 00:05:28,418
Don't touch me. Get out now!

97
00:05:30,411 --> 00:05:33,023
I'll leave after changing the dressing.
Here, be good.

98
00:05:33,064 --> 00:05:35,399
I don't want you to do it.
I don't want you to do it.

99
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,977
Get out!

100
00:05:38,018 --> 00:05:39,400
Get out!

101
00:05:39,441 --> 00:05:40,413
Xiao Jun.

102
00:05:40,454 --> 00:05:41,567
Xiao Jun, what's wrong?

103
00:05:41,608 --> 00:05:42,788
Dr. Xia, what's going on?

104
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:44,190
Nothing.

105
00:05:44,976 --> 00:05:48,610
Dr. Xia, you need to learn
how to respect your patient.

106
00:05:53,585 --> 00:05:55,440
What if the patient is wrong?

107
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:57,399
If he stays stubborn,

108
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,180
he will bear greater pain in the end.

109
00:05:59,652 --> 00:06:01,855
Dr. Xia, it's just changing the dressing.

110
00:06:01,896 --> 00:06:03,916
Why would he suffer from greater pain?

111
00:06:06,688 --> 00:06:07,568
Nothing.

112
00:06:07,609 --> 00:06:08,749
I'll come again later.

113
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:09,970
Sure.

114
00:06:11,902 --> 00:06:13,877
Why hasn't medical order
for patient no. 17 here yet?

115
00:06:13,918 --> 00:06:15,739
You're the slowest. Speed up.

116
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:17,068
No...

117
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,916
My desktop went dead just now.

118
00:06:18,957 --> 00:06:20,087
I just got it repaired.

119
00:06:20,128 --> 00:06:21,400
Explain to the patient!

120
00:06:39,158 --> 00:06:41,388
Can you please change dressing
for Luo Xiao Jun on behalf of me?

121
00:06:41,602 --> 00:06:43,062
No, I'm occupied.

122
00:06:44,696 --> 00:06:45,996
I'll prepare the medical order for you.

123
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,421
You can leave all the medical orders that
has to be done within this week to me.

124
00:06:54,038 --> 00:06:55,120
Two weeks worth of medical orders.

125
00:06:55,656 --> 00:06:56,536
It's a deal.

126
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,200
It's done.

127
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,840
-Thank you, Dr. Xiao.
-No problem.

128
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,710
Thank you.

129
00:07:09,036 --> 00:07:10,466
By the way, Xiao Jun,

130
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,520
tell me the truth.

131
00:07:12,977 --> 00:07:15,227
Why won't you let Dr. Xia
to change your dressing?

132
00:07:15,486 --> 00:07:16,800
It's none of your business.

133
00:07:17,905 --> 00:07:19,485
It's none of your business too.

134
00:07:20,191 --> 00:07:21,352
Luo Xiao Jun!

135
00:07:21,393 --> 00:07:22,393
What's wrong with you?

136
00:07:22,434 --> 00:07:23,904
You're being rude.

137
00:07:27,191 --> 00:07:28,211
Liang Mu Ze.

138
00:07:28,609 --> 00:07:30,268
Will you take care of Ms. Zhen forever?

139
00:07:31,891 --> 00:07:33,151
It's none of your business.

140
00:07:33,473 --> 00:07:34,483
Xiao Jun.

141
00:07:34,572 --> 00:07:37,543
You haven't told me
what you want for lunch.

142
00:07:38,169 --> 00:07:39,338
Will you, Liang Mu Ze?

143
00:07:39,857 --> 00:07:41,800
Of course. Do you have to ask?

144
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,696
I want braised pork ribs.
Two portions please.

145
00:07:45,737 --> 00:07:47,640
Ms. Zhen, go with Liang Mu Ze.

146
00:07:58,496 --> 00:08:00,240
Why are you so happy?

147
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,480
Liang Mu Ze promised
to take care of Ms. Zhen forever.

148
00:08:06,486 --> 00:08:07,480
What does that mean?

149
00:08:08,353 --> 00:08:10,640
That means I took note of it.

150
00:08:13,681 --> 00:08:15,461
I know why you hate me.

151
00:08:16,136 --> 00:08:18,120
It's because of Liang Mu Ze, right?

152
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,040
Listen.

153
00:08:22,671 --> 00:08:24,935
Ever since we met each other
for the first time,

154
00:08:24,976 --> 00:08:26,516
I've always been your doctor.

155
00:08:26,997 --> 00:08:28,186
Now, I'm still your doctor.

156
00:08:28,677 --> 00:08:31,668
I'll be responsible of your health
until you're discharged.

157
00:08:32,105 --> 00:08:33,684
Please don't hate me.

158
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,569
It's nothing to do with Liang Mu Ze.

159
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,059
It's for your own good.

160
00:08:39,577 --> 00:08:40,507
If...

161
00:08:41,588 --> 00:08:43,759
You hold grudges against me for nothing,

162
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:45,900
you may hurt yourself in the end.

163
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:48,009
Please buy me a bouquet of flowers.

164
00:08:48,284 --> 00:08:49,160
What?

165
00:08:49,695 --> 00:08:51,065
In the name of Liang Mu Ze.

166
00:08:51,423 --> 00:08:53,493
Send a bouquet of flowers to my mom.

167
00:08:54,344 --> 00:08:56,084
That way, I'll believe in you.

168
00:08:56,431 --> 00:08:58,421
Will you behave and receive treatment?

169
00:08:58,462 --> 00:08:59,342
Yes.

170
00:09:01,294 --> 00:09:02,194
That's a deal.

171
00:09:03,576 --> 00:09:04,476
That's a deal.

172
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,660
-Are you going back to the camp later?
-Yes.

173
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,780
Xiao Jun becomes more sensitive
after falling sick.

174
00:09:12,019 --> 00:09:14,310
Don't take what he said just now
to heart.

175
00:09:15,513 --> 00:09:16,403
Meng Zhen.

176
00:09:16,745 --> 00:09:19,125
Xiao Jun is a kid but I'm not.

177
00:09:19,313 --> 00:09:20,893
I'll honor my words.

178
00:09:22,058 --> 00:09:23,598
You don't have to do that, Mu Ze.

179
00:09:25,976 --> 00:09:28,116
It's been eight years.
It's more than enough.

180
00:09:30,302 --> 00:09:31,498
I can take care of myself.

181
00:09:31,539 --> 00:09:33,128
Xiao Jun has grown up.

182
00:09:33,169 --> 00:09:34,789
I can take care of him by myself.

183
00:09:35,377 --> 00:09:36,277
As for you,

184
00:09:36,863 --> 00:09:38,043
you should move on.

185
00:09:38,436 --> 00:09:39,879
You should go on with dating,
getting married...

186
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:40,820
and have your own children.

187
00:09:41,369 --> 00:09:43,241
You should find your own life purpose.

188
00:09:43,282 --> 00:09:44,942
Taking care of you is my life purpose.

189
00:09:45,869 --> 00:09:47,879
Do you plan to live like this
for the rest of your life?

190
00:09:51,432 --> 00:09:53,482
Both of us know that
it shouldn't be like this.

191
00:09:54,035 --> 00:09:55,229
Sometimes,

192
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,690
inappropriate promises
could be a form of disturbance...

193
00:09:59,233 --> 00:10:00,733
to a kid.

194
00:10:02,288 --> 00:10:03,178
Mom.

195
00:10:03,435 --> 00:10:04,315
Xiao Jun.

196
00:10:04,659 --> 00:10:06,099
Xiao Jun, why are you here?

197
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:07,710
Didn't I tell you to wait in the ward?

198
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:10,250
It's for you.

199
00:10:10,869 --> 00:10:12,339
Where did you get the flowers?

200
00:10:12,535 --> 00:10:14,035
Liang Mu Ze got it in secret.

201
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,540
He wants to give you a surprise. Look.

202
00:10:17,031 --> 00:10:18,891
It's a card with his name on it.

203
00:10:23,854 --> 00:10:25,040
Hurry up, Liang Mu Ze.

204
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:26,560
Aren't you going to propose?

205
00:10:34,127 --> 00:10:35,267
The flowers are so beautiful.

206
00:10:35,489 --> 00:10:36,462
I like it.

207
00:10:36,503 --> 00:10:38,203
I like it no matter who the sender is.

208
00:10:38,458 --> 00:10:39,678
However...

209
00:10:40,158 --> 00:10:41,748
We can't get married.

210
00:10:46,653 --> 00:10:47,673
Why?

211
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,580
You promised
you will take care of her forever.

212
00:10:49,843 --> 00:10:51,353
I'll take care of both of you forever.

213
00:10:51,394 --> 00:10:53,054
However,
it's different from getting married.

214
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,160
Why?

215
00:10:58,167 --> 00:10:59,360
Is it because you don't like my mom?

216
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,060
Here, come here.

217
00:11:03,339 --> 00:11:04,294
Listen.

218
00:11:04,335 --> 00:11:05,200
Come here.

219
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,320
Sit down.

220
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,209
Let me tell you.

221
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:18,670
Marriage is something important.

222
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:22,488
It's not as simple as you imagine.

223
00:11:22,529 --> 00:11:24,899
It's not just about liking someone or not.

224
00:11:25,694 --> 00:11:27,994
There are more elements to it.

225
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,480
Therefore,

226
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,520
I can't marry Liang Mu Ze.

227
00:11:34,219 --> 00:11:35,469
It's not going to happen.

228
00:11:35,658 --> 00:11:36,680
Can you understand?

229
00:11:39,430 --> 00:11:41,770
He promised to take care of you forever.

230
00:11:42,592 --> 00:11:44,602
He said that out of kindness.

231
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,420
However, taking care of us
is not his responsibility.

232
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,330
It's a success!

233
00:12:02,909 --> 00:12:04,769
Stop crying, Xiao Jun.

234
00:12:04,810 --> 00:12:06,480
Stop crying.

235
00:12:06,803 --> 00:12:07,943
Xiao Jun.

236
00:12:12,146 --> 00:12:13,026
What's wrong?

237
00:12:13,788 --> 00:12:14,768
What's wrong?

238
00:12:15,238 --> 00:12:16,280
Was it you?

239
00:12:17,265 --> 00:12:18,127
Yes.

240
00:12:18,168 --> 00:12:19,068
Are you crazy?

241
00:12:19,553 --> 00:12:20,613
Ridiculous.

242
00:12:25,056 --> 00:12:25,936
Yes.

243
00:12:26,203 --> 00:12:27,263
I'm crazy.

244
00:12:28,311 --> 00:12:29,291
Dr. Xia.

245
00:12:29,496 --> 00:12:31,000
You should apologise to her.

246
00:12:33,727 --> 00:12:34,707
Dr. Xia.

247
00:12:36,439 --> 00:12:38,705
Dr. Xia, sorry to have taken up
so much of your time.

248
00:12:38,746 --> 00:12:40,552
It's okay. I'm going to meet a friend
at the emergency department.

249
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,870
Be careful!

250
00:12:43,612 --> 00:12:45,152
Dr. Xia, are you okay?

251
00:12:46,686 --> 00:12:48,026
Put up with it.

252
00:12:48,691 --> 00:12:51,812
Your bone is fine
but the ligament is injured.

253
00:12:52,087 --> 00:12:54,432
If it's not fixed, it won't recover.

254
00:12:54,473 --> 00:12:56,574
You're a doctor.
You should know the consequences.

255
00:12:57,768 --> 00:12:59,208
How long will it take to recover?

256
00:12:59,559 --> 00:13:00,619
It will take about a week.

257
00:13:00,816 --> 00:13:02,666
Don't walk too much and rest well.

258
00:13:03,556 --> 00:13:05,016
Can I go to work tomorrow?

259
00:13:05,266 --> 00:13:06,162
Go to work?

260
00:13:06,203 --> 00:13:07,780
Do you plan to give up
on conducting surgery?

261
00:13:07,821 --> 00:13:09,153
We'll talk about it
when your leg has fully recovered.

262
00:13:14,899 --> 00:13:16,690
You may get back to work.

263
00:13:16,731 --> 00:13:18,000
I can handle it.

264
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,162
I'm going back to the unit at 6:00.

265
00:13:20,203 --> 00:13:21,303
You should come back with me.

266
00:13:21,844 --> 00:13:22,724
Why?

267
00:13:22,765 --> 00:13:23,690
You'll be staying there for a few days.

268
00:13:23,929 --> 00:13:24,829
Why?

269
00:13:24,909 --> 00:13:27,259
Why? He's worried about you.

270
00:13:28,890 --> 00:13:29,790
No.

271
00:13:30,696 --> 00:13:33,415
I promised Zhang Yi Chi
to take good care of you.

272
00:13:35,148 --> 00:13:36,084
It's done.

273
00:13:36,125 --> 00:13:37,265
Go get a wheelchair.

274
00:13:37,391 --> 00:13:38,271
It's not needed.

