I'll always be in the camp.

552
00:30:16,260 --> 00:30:18,680
You can reach me anytime for anything.

553
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:19,780
Okay?

554
00:30:20,651 --> 00:30:21,531
Xia Chu.

555
00:30:32,710 --> 00:30:33,590
I'm hungry.

556
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:36,300
No problem.

557
00:30:48,992 --> 00:30:49,922
Reporting!

558
00:30:51,642 --> 00:30:52,542
Come in.

559
00:30:56,010 --> 00:30:57,040
Captain Liang.

560
00:30:59,798 --> 00:31:02,108
Why do you look troubled?

561
00:31:03,351 --> 00:31:04,881
Look at the operational requirement
suggested by the sixth team.

562
00:31:04,922 --> 00:31:06,022
How can I not be troubled?

563
00:31:07,849 --> 00:31:10,269
I'm not talking about
operational requirement.

564
00:31:12,847 --> 00:31:14,257
I'm talking about Dr. Xia.

565
00:31:15,299 --> 00:31:16,369
She's a lady after all.

566
00:31:16,550 --> 00:31:17,850
She's staying at the guest house alone.

567
00:31:17,891 --> 00:31:19,111
Do you think it's appropriate?

568
00:31:19,490 --> 00:31:21,590
Dr. Xia is a doctor.

569
00:31:21,631 --> 00:31:23,341
She knows how to take care of herself.

570
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:24,560
Why are you doing this to her?

571
00:31:24,601 --> 00:31:26,231
You're used to staying with her.

572
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:29,800
-Lieutenant Tian.
-Yes!

573
00:31:30,130 --> 00:31:33,170
I think our platoon
is lacking vigor lately.

574
00:31:34,318 --> 00:31:35,198
Is it?

575
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:38,160
I was receiving training elsewhere.

576
00:31:39,112 --> 00:31:40,449
As the vice captain,

577
00:31:40,490 --> 00:31:42,320
aren't you supposed to lead by example...

578
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,837
and make sure everyone in the platoon...

579
00:31:44,878 --> 00:31:46,610
including yourself
to be disciplined in physical training?

580
00:31:46,650 --> 00:31:48,051
Look at your
physical fitness test results.

581
00:31:48,092 --> 00:31:49,072
What happened to you?

582
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:51,400
However, the overall performance
of our platoon has improved.

583
00:31:52,189 --> 00:31:54,600
Xiao Teng won the second runner-up
in 800m obstacle race.

584
00:31:54,641 --> 00:31:55,731
-Is that good enough?
-No.

585
00:31:55,772 --> 00:31:57,312
-Is that good enough?
-No!

586
00:31:58,990 --> 00:32:00,930
From tomorrow onward,
train yourself to death.

587
00:32:00,971 --> 00:32:02,961
Make sure you get number one
in the next assessment.

588
00:32:03,002 --> 00:32:04,362
-Do you hear me?
-Yes!

589
00:32:05,799 --> 00:32:06,789
Leave.

590
00:32:07,175 --> 00:32:08,055
Yes.

591
00:32:42,769 --> 00:32:46,239
♪Standing upright and neatly lined up
under the scorching sun♪

592
00:32:46,280 --> 00:32:49,660
♪Heads up in the strong wind
and act boldly as usual♪

593
00:32:49,701 --> 00:32:53,081
♪Unafraid of the challenges and dangers.
Our generation is invincible♪

594
00:32:53,121 --> 00:32:56,058
♪We trust each other♪

595
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:59,807
♪Dive into danger like a swordfish
diving into the deep ocean♪

596
00:32:59,848 --> 00:33:03,368
♪Flying a fighter jet like
a bold eagle soaring high in the sky♪

597
00:33:03,409 --> 00:33:06,799
♪Trekking through forests
and over mountains♪

598
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:10,220
♪Our passion burns the thorns down♪

599
00:33:10,261 --> 00:33:11,579
♪We've always been naughty brats♪

600
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:13,616
♪We know we have great responsibilities
even though we haven't grown up♪

601
00:33:13,657 --> 00:33:14,667
♪Endless, dull repetitions♪

602
00:33:14,708 --> 00:33:16,640
♪It's to make sure we don't hesitate
when danger strikes♪

603
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,360
♪Throbbing disappears
in a blink of an eye♪

604
00:33:18,401 --> 00:33:20,080
♪Know that there's no second chance
on the battlefield♪

605
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,578
♪Relentlessly looking
at each other again and again♪

606
00:33:21,619 --> 00:33:24,779
♪It's to make sure we don't surrender
to fate♪

607
00:33:27,320 --> 00:33:30,680
♪Concentrate the firepower
in the face of a strong enemy♪

608
00:33:30,721 --> 00:33:34,199
♪You and I fight fiercely♪

609
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:37,680
♪We are fearless even when
we are confronted with calamity♪

610
00:33:37,721 --> 00:33:41,000
♪You and I fight fiercely♪

611
00:33:41,041 --> 00:33:46,359
♪The stability and peace
of all places in the world♪

612
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,460
He's showing off.

613
00:33:49,970 --> 00:33:50,870
So?

614
00:33:51,130 --> 00:33:53,950
Have you gotten any the idea
for the coming shoot?

615
00:33:55,090 --> 00:33:56,800
Let me know if you have any ideas.

616
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:59,860
Boss, why don't we film
about internet entrepreneurship?

617
00:34:03,268 --> 00:34:04,488
How about acting agencies?

618
00:34:04,892 --> 00:34:06,142
Why don't we go for food column?

619
00:34:10,047 --> 00:34:10,927
Mi Gu!

620
00:34:13,599 --> 00:34:14,619
Are you okay?

621
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:16,118
What do you think?

622
00:34:16,159 --> 00:34:17,349
I didn't mean it.

623
00:34:17,630 --> 00:34:19,900
Something went wrong with your guest.

624
00:34:19,941 --> 00:34:21,691
Not only did you not solve the issue,

625
00:34:22,130 --> 00:34:23,369
you dozed off during the meeting.

626
00:34:23,410 --> 00:34:24,710
Do you still want the job?

627
00:34:25,626 --> 00:34:26,589
Boss.

628
00:34:26,630 --> 00:34:28,490
I've completed the new proposal.

629
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:35,000
Please take a look.

630
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,849
Filming a doctor's daily life?

631
00:34:41,808 --> 00:34:43,308
Filming a doctor's daily life...

632
00:34:43,349 --> 00:34:45,729
to present the doctor-patient relationship
which is a public concern.

633
00:34:45,770 --> 00:34:47,490
We can also make the show stands out...

634
00:34:47,531 --> 00:34:48,860
by including all kinds
of eye catching rare diseases.

635
00:34:48,901 --> 00:34:49,935
At the same time, we can instil...

636
00:34:49,976 --> 00:34:52,110
the correct values on health and death
in the public.

637
00:34:52,813 --> 00:34:55,069
Not only is it evergreen,
it's also interesting to watch.

638
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:56,777
More importantly,
I have a good subject to feature.

639
00:34:57,370 --> 00:34:58,250
What do you think?

640
00:34:58,605 --> 00:34:59,915
Do you think it's doable?

641
00:35:02,627 --> 00:35:03,507
Yes.

642
00:35:04,150 --> 00:35:05,030
Lad.

643
00:35:05,849 --> 00:35:08,290
Your mom is exhausted
from taking care of you.

644
00:35:08,721 --> 00:35:10,037
Now that you're discharged,

645
00:35:10,078 --> 00:35:11,691
you must listen to your mom.

646
00:35:11,732 --> 00:35:12,619
Got it?

647
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:13,540
Yes.

648
00:35:14,066 --> 00:35:14,986
All right, Dr. Zhang.

649
00:35:15,027 --> 00:35:16,247
You don't have to send us off.

650
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:18,170
Send me a message
after you've reached home.

651
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:19,572
Sure.

652
00:35:19,613 --> 00:35:21,233
Xiao Jun, say goodbye to Dr. Zhang.

653
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:22,840
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

654
00:35:23,638 --> 00:35:24,518
Let's go.

655
00:35:32,525 --> 00:35:35,705
Dr. Zhang, you're indeed not picky at all.

656
00:35:37,690 --> 00:35:39,380
My patient is discharged today.

657
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,050
Am I not allowed to send him off?

658
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:43,880
Why didn't you come that weekend?

659
00:35:45,735 --> 00:35:46,995
You went there?

660
00:35:47,036 --> 00:35:47,997
Of course.

661
00:35:48,038 --> 00:35:49,508
I waited for you for the whole night.

662
00:35:50,326 --> 00:35:51,666
No way.

663
00:35:51,707 --> 00:35:53,367
I'm serious. Why would I lie?

664
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:55,040
I know you well.

665
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:56,440
Li Juan.

666
00:35:56,559 --> 00:35:57,569
You...

667
00:35:58,560 --> 00:36:00,820
You're anything but stubborn.

668
00:36:01,130 --> 00:36:03,489
Even if you waited at the pub
for the whole night,

669
00:36:03,530 --> 00:36:05,540
you're not just waiting for me, right?

670
00:36:06,741 --> 00:36:07,669
We had a date.

671
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:09,560
Who else would I wait for
if it weren't for you?

672
00:36:09,710 --> 00:36:11,490
Are you crazy?

673
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:17,960
Are you free tonight? Let's go together.

674
00:36:23,490 --> 00:36:24,470
I'm sorry.

675
00:36:25,107 --> 00:36:26,487
I already have a date.

676
00:36:28,990 --> 00:36:30,979
Sure, can't wait to eat it.

677
00:36:31,020 --> 00:36:32,110
See you tonight.

678
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:36,490
See?

679
00:36:37,110 --> 00:36:38,740
I have everything in the world.

680
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:56,010
I took care of the surveillance system.

681
00:37:36,750 --> 00:37:37,722
I'm ready.

682
00:37:39,336 --> 00:37:40,796
Do you really want to do that?

683
00:39:01,901 --> 00:39:04,774
("The Tokyo Zodiac Murders"
by Soji Shimada)

684
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:10,740
Listen.

685
00:39:11,353 --> 00:39:12,983
I have a bad hunch.

686
00:39:13,554 --> 00:39:14,760
You'd better be fast.

687
00:39:26,983 --> 00:39:28,960
Are you done?

688
00:39:49,409 --> 00:39:51,389
Can you hear me?

689
00:39:51,430 --> 00:39:54,013
Will you answer me?

690
00:39:56,487 --> 00:39:58,375
Can you hear me, Zhuo Ran?

691
00:39:58,416 --> 00:39:59,994
Can you hear me?

692
00:40:00,035 --> 00:40:01,960
Can you hear me?

693
00:40:25,010 --> 00:40:26,550
Are you Xia Chu's pet?

694
00:40:33,750 --> 00:40:35,010
What is your name?

695
00:40:35,730 --> 00:40:37,040
Don't touch me.

696
00:40:42,468 --> 00:40:44,008
I didn't know that you had a cat.

697
00:42:15,501 --> 00:42:16,993
Can you hear me? Yang Mu Ze is back.

698
00:42:17,041 --> 00:42:18,409
Zhuo Ran, can you hear me?
Liang Mu Ze...

699
00:42:18,450 --> 00:42:19,670
Liang Mu Ze is back!

700
00:42:20,060 --> 00:42:21,920
Can you hear me? Liang Mu Ze is back!

701
00:43:19,689 --> 00:43:21,227
-What's wrong?
-Help!

702
00:43:21,267 --> 00:43:22,847
A bad guy wanted to hurt me.

703
00:43:22,887 --> 00:43:24,787
A bad guy is after me!

704
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:27,550
Are you missing your owner?

705
00:43:28,500 --> 00:43:30,160
She'll be back soon.

706
00:43:31,298 --> 00:43:33,288
That's enough. Go watch the door.

707
00:43:33,329 --> 00:43:34,601
I don't care if she's coming back soon.

708
00:43:34,641 --> 00:43:37,061
I want you to take me away from here.

709
00:44:25,560 --> 00:44:27,810
Can we rewind to the earlier time?

710
00:44:28,119 --> 00:44:29,001
Usually it works that way.

711
00:44:29,042 --> 00:44:31,161
However, something is wrong
with the surveillance system.

712
00:44:31,201 --> 00:44:32,861
There is no video signal.

713
00:44:33,677 --> 00:44:34,678
No signal?

714
00:44:34,719 --> 00:44:36,370
Yes.
We just got it repaired.

715
00:44:36,411 --> 00:44:38,041
Hence,
the earlier recording is not available.

716
00:44:38,081 --> 00:44:39,011
Sorry about that.
